@token = Bearer 

### ==================================== ###
### 🔐 AUTH ROUTES
### ====================================

# 🔑 Login
POST http://localhost:5010/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "arrafi",
  "password": "123"
}

###

# 🔁 Refresh Token
GET http://localhost:5010/token

###

# 🚪 Logout
DELETE http://localhost:5010/logout
Authorization: {{token}}

